  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="FR">DRR Network &#x96; Small Action Credit 2013-2014</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="FR">The DRR small action credit line enables timely, efficient and solution-oriented funding of short-term and non-recurring DRR initiatives and internventions that enhance the overall objective of disaster resilience and integral risk management. The promotion, the safe-guarding and the institutional mainstreaming of DRR knowledge&#xA0; is a key goal of the DRR network. It is through the DRR Network&#x92;s knowledge management efforts that an effective transfer to the field and into SDC&#x92;s programmes and those of its multilateral and bilateral partners takes place. DRR-related interventions contribute to SDC&#x92;s objective of transcending its strategies and programmes which again enhances SDC&#x92;s international role as a leading actor in the field of DRR. It further allows for an extensive valorization of Swiss thematic expertise.</narrative>
  </description>
